      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-6 to">
        <h2>Robotics Club</h2>
      <p>exploring new territories in the field of robotics
        learn, experiment, and experience the joy of being a roboticist.</p>
      <hr>
      <p class="p3text">
        The Robotics Club began in the year 2021, and has had a successful sprint in this AY. The club was started as an intitiative to facilitate students understanding, design, and concepts about robotics The club recruited new members in July 2021 A total of 45 new members were inducted into the club after rigorous tests and interviews. The club had organized a Mini Project Competition for its members. It was held from August to November 2022. Around 50 people from the second and third years participated in the competition. The main aim of the Mini Project Competition was to put to test the practical skills and coordination of the club members The participants took part in the competition by forming teams of 5 people. Each team preferably included members from all the 3- divisions (CCI, EDP, MDF)
        The Club has 3 student bodies, dealing with Mechanical, Electronics and Programming elements of Robotics respectfully.
